---
title: Birchermuesli
image:
source: 
course: Breakfast
servings: 2
---

Grate @apple{1} and stir together with @mixed oats{0.5%cup}, @hazelnuts{0.125%cup}(chopped), and @milk{.25%cup}. Let sit for 5 minutes.

Mix in @frozen berries or finely chopped peach{0.5%cup} and @plain whole milk yogurt{1%cup}.

If desired, add mashed @banana{} to sweeten or @lemon juice{} to tarten.

Cover and let sit in fridge overnight.